Postoji* mnogo oblika umetnosti. (There are many forms of art.)

Postoje* stvari koje se više ne mogu ispraviti. (There are things that can no longer be fixed.)

Postojala* je ogromna biblioteka u gradu. (There was a huge library in the city.)

Postojiće* mnogo izazova u budućnosti. (There will be many challenges in the future.)

Postojala su* dva načina da se reši problem. (There were two ways to solve the problem.)